Dinner

Dinner service is available Monday through Saturday starting at 5:00pm, and our dinner menu* features an eclectic collection of American fare—fresh seafood, beloved comfort food and seasonal dishes. We even have a secret stash of chicken fingers for the pickiest of palates.

*Please note that the dinner menu on this page is subject to availability.
